2001-04-26 probably somewhat out of date

		       SICStus Library Modules
		       -----------------------

How to build
------------

Build from toplevel directory (..) using the following commands:

% make lib

or to build specific modules

% make lib MODULES="clpfd.po jasper.po tcltk.po"


Files
-----

Makefile		Makefile for this directory.
Makefile_<xxx>		Automatically generated makefile fragments
			for building the foreign resources
genmakefile.pl		Perl-script to generate the Makefile_xxx files
README			This text.

arrays.pl		Array manipulation routines.
assoc.pl		AVL Tree Implementaion of Association Lists.
atts.pl			Attributed variables.
charsio.pl		I/O on lists of character codes.
charsio.c		C code for charsio.
clpb.pl			clp(B) constraint solver.
clpfd/, clpfd.pl	clp(FD) constraint solver.
clpq/, clpq.pl		clp(Q) constraint solver.
clpqr/,			clp(Q,R) constraint solvers common.
clpr/, clpr.pl		clp(R) constraint solver.
db/, db.pl		Persistent Fact Storage Facility.
fastrw.pl		Fast I/O of terms.
fastrw.c		C code for fastrw.
fastrw.h		C headers for fastrw.
fdbg.pl			Finite domain constraint tracer.
flinkage.pl		Support for creating flinkage.c files.
gauge.pl		The Gauge profiling tool.
gauge.txt		Gauge Help text
heaps.pl		Priority queues.
jasper/, jasper.pl	Java-Prolog interface
linda/			Linda---Process communication.
lists.pl		List Processing predicates.
mkindex.pl		Library index generator.
objects/, objects.pl	Prolog Objects.
ordsets.pl		Ordered set manipulation.
pow.pl			Prolog Objects Windows.
queues.pl		Queue operations.
random.pl		Random number generator.
random.c		C code for random numbers.
sockets.pl		Socket operations.
sockets.c		C code for socket operations.
system.pl		OS interface utilites.
system.c		OS interface utilites for UNIX.
systos2.c		OS interface utilites for OS/2.
systw32.c		OS interface utilites for Win32.
tcltk.pl		Tcl/Tk language/toolkit interface.
tcltk/			Tcl/Tk interface C code.
terms.pl		Term utilities.
timeout.pl		Timeout primitive.
timeout.c		C code for timeout primitive.
tkconsole.tcl, tkconsole.pl	   Tcl/Tk source consol.
tkterm.tcl	        Tcl/Tk terminal window.
trees.pl		Updatable binary trees.
ugraphs.pl		Unweighted Graph processing utilities.
vbsp/, vbsp.pl		Visual Basic Interface
wgraphs.pl		Weighted Graph processing utilities.
xref.pl			Cross referencer.

Obsolete stuff:
gcla/			Generalized Horn Clause Language.
makefile.bc		Makefile for Borland C.
makefile.msc		Makefile for Microsoft C.
makefile.wat		Makefile for Watcom C.
makefile.bc		d:o, Win32-Borland
makefile.msc		d:o, Win32-Visual C++
mkos2emx		Makefile for OS/2.
